Development
-----------

Please make sure that you have SASS installed. 
Un UNIX environment you can fire up SASS compiler with `make` command. 
In Windows run this is console:
  $ sass --watch src/bauhaus.sass:dist/bauhaus.css
  
Or just use any UI helpers for SASS like Scout [1] or Koala [2]

[1] - http://mhs.github.io/scout-app/
[2] - http://koala-app.com
